headline: GTA Online Update
subtitle: Welcome to the High Life
content:
New Luxury Condos for sale.

You can now add a second property to your real estate portfolio. Visit www.dynasty8realestate.com to see all the stunning Apartments on offer.

As well as properties you may already be familiar with, you’ll find a new, very desirable high-end apartment available in many of Los Santos’ most luxurious residences - complete with an additional 10 car Garage to store even more vehicles.
